{"tid":908338,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"忍無可忍，真係仁慈夠","createTime":"2018-11-19T13:34:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T17:57:03.000Z","uid":222884,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3d547f27f91cda66906c4c4303e634ec41724773","tid":908338,"uid":222884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T13:34:18.000Z","msg":"幾個月前喺一個app識咗個人前後呃咗$6000, 之後以死要脅，唔肯還錢，然後一直拖。<br />\n<br />\n件事發生喺八月尾，本身已經冇再同呢個人講嘢，但有一日佢問可唔可以借住三千先，有緊要事，幾日內會還返。我問，點樣make sure 你唔係呃錢，佢就影咗張身分證俾我叫我可以去報警。<br />\n<br />\n問佢發生咩事，佢話佢俾屋企人趕咗出門口，啱啱喺外國返嚟又咩朋友都冇曬，所以要啲錢去租屋住，份糧唔夠俾，ok, 咁我心軟就借多$2000俾佢。<br />\n<br />\n過多幾日，又問我可唔可以借多一千，因為佢連搭車返工嘅錢都冇，如果唔係就還唔到錢俾我，我認我戇鳩，最後都係借咗。<br />\n<br />\n好明顯佢幾日內一定還唔到啦咁，佢話要下個月出咗糧先還到，不過都會盡還，有咁多還咁多咁。我就戇鳩到話，既然係咁，不如每個月還$500, 分十幾次還？咁樣burden會細啲 (其實已經幾乎唔洗佢還咁)<br />\n<br />\n好啦，十月催咗一次，佢就話15號先出糧。等到15號，催咗幾次都唔認機，直到我話要報警，佢就話自己唔係有心避，而係佢俾人炒咗，要準備去死，唔好逼佢。<br />\n<br />\n其實我真係好蠢，仲肯同佢negotiate到十一月二十號一定要還到，如果唔係就放曬佢所有嘢上連登。如我所料，今次搵佢，佢又有無限個excuse <br />\n<br />\n我真係忍夠<br />\n<br />\n想講呢$6000對我嚟講絕對唔係一筆細數，我返兩個月part time 先儲到，而且佢都知，我儲起啲錢係要嚟去exchange <br />\n<br />\n最sad係，早排由android 機轉咗去iPhone, 啲WhatsApp chat record 冇曬，得返少量screenshots 同佢啲資料，仲有我入錢俾佢嘅證據 (如下)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SybJWPB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSybJWPB.png&h=fc848ec7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一次入咗$3000<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rOzfNWX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrOzfNWX.png&h=df404981&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第二次入嗰$2000我戇鳩到唔記得print advice, 不過喺ebanking 搵得返個record <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cDosD26.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcDosD26.png&h=4c993ff6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第三次入咗$1000<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TQSdzCu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTQSdzCu.png&h=8bb4ce95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前講到20/11之前一定要還到第一筆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4XgND4A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4XgND4A.png&h=109fd06c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n宜家去追就喺度搵藉口<br />\n<br />\n賤人個樣，認住佢，成日chur 人同佢扑嘢㗎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9fvCgU8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9fvCgU8.png&h=5abe0ab3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c24982f730ee7ceca4e84a330114ca61ab31fe5e","tid":908338,"uid":176890,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T13:35:32.000Z","msg":"人_無藥醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f581fee2936ff34f3bf21aa143b63c3581578428","tid":908338,"uid":201604,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T13:36:53.000Z","msg":"你都係條蠢豬閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb4081a0db9ed460290e982ce5535a7778fd8808","tid":908338,"uid":6424,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T13:37:12.000Z","msg":"唔係話想Blame the victim <br />\n但樓主真係好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拎得返最好，拎唔返就幾千當上一課<br />\n唔係可能下一次就幾十幾百萬上新聞"},{"pid":"056f0c026c2e1c5374cfef2cbb1f295130d40506","tid":908338,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T13:38:15.000Z","msg":"咩app黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 交友app?"},{"pid":"f37c1bd50463e6d70f5706d86b05a46e69440585","tid":908338,"uid":78595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T13:42:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6d2f93b20c7689c71fb153ccb492e38ac0cf26d7","tid":908338,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f37c1bd50463e6d70f5706d86b05a46e69440585","tid":908338,"uid":78595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"056f0c026c2e1c5374cfef2cbb1f295130d40506","tid":908338,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T1